profile:
OGC - Ottawa General Contractors are leaders as Ottawa's design and build renovation experts. Specializing in home renovations, new and custom home construction as well as home design. With our project management and coordination, we're able to efficiently juggle more jobs, large and small, without dropping the ball. 

Ottawa General Contractors are an accredited business with the Ottawa BBB and our CEO, Moe Abbas is a former member of the board of directors for the Better Business Bureau (BBB).. Our skills and expert service has allowed us to expand to other cities in Canada including Vancouver and Calgary in less than 8 years making us one of the fastest growing construction companies. 

We offer warranty following the Tarion warranty guidelines for all our renovations and construction projects. We also have a design center and in house designers available to help you design and build your home. With over 50 years of experience, our team has the knowledge, the tools, the skill-set and the resources to give you the best value for your dollar at unbeatable service. 

We at Ottawa General Contractors understand that you are looking for value with your renovation services. Trust our team to do it right the first time! Call us directly at (613) 225-9991!

Visit our website for all our credentials and more information.

profile:
Smart Space is a professional organizing service dedicated to helping individuals, families, and organizations achieve greater productivity, reduced stress, and enhanced well-being.

We help our clients with the physical aspect of organizing by providing consulting services, both virtually and in homes, home offices, and businesses throughout Eastern Ontario. In addition, we also provide educational services through our workshops and seminars.

Furthermore, because we believe that organization and productivity are critical to your professional and personal well-being, we offer coaching services to help you to develop new habits that will keep you focused and organized.

We have been developing solutions that are customized to suit the unique needs of each client since 1999.
name: Smart Space Organizing Inc.

profile:
As a full-service Audio Visual company that offers a wide range of custom-tailored products and services, the capabilities of Capello Systems reach far and wide.
Our integrated Audio Visual systems and solutions will excite the senses with unparalleled sight and sound to completely transform your event or venue. With best-in-class products and components, we use our expertise to take our clients’ security and communications capabilities to the next level for a diverse array of applications and settings.
We are very focused on giving clients what they need by doing everything in-house, hence our heavy involvement during each phase of our projects. This means that clients can count on our experienced staff to ensure the project’s success from consultation and system design to installation, training, support and on-going service. Maintaining a high level of quality control is as important to us as it is to our clients.
Our talented team of engineers, technologists, account managers, and administrators comes into work every day motivated to deliver solutions to the client’s complete satisfaction. Our commitment to designing and building quality integrated Audio Visual, communication and security systems has allowed us to thrive for more than five decades in the National Capital Region. Reaching such a huge milestone is a great source of pride, something that will continue to drive the business as we look to the bright and exciting future ahead.
name: Capello Systems Ltd.
